---
title: Easy Honey Mustard Pork with Roasted Pumpkin & Apple Salad
description: This classic honey mustard combo brings so much flavour to juicy pork steaks. Serve them with sweet
roasted veggies and a crisp apple salad for a winning low-carb dinner.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
